item.title: Carol Blood for governor 2022
item.description: Carol Blood for governor My name is Carol Blood. Iâ€™m a Nebraskan, born and raised. I was born in McCook, Nebraska, raised in rural Adams County, Nebraska and raised my family in Sarpy County, Nebraska. My husband Joe and I have been married for 34 years and are blessed with three adult children and 10 grandchildren. I love my community and have been an active volunteer and community advocate for decades.
